E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Hamburger Postulate: Leonard thinks he's been wasting his time on Penny, so he turns his attention to Leslie. Sheldon's uncomfortable with a change to his hamburger routine. (S1 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Solder Excursion Diversion: Sheldon makes a surprise revelation when Amy buys him a new laptop. Leonard and Howard lie to their wives to avoid an errand. (S9 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Big Bear Precipitation: Sheldon shares a secret about Leonard when the two of them go on a weekend trip to a cabin in the country with Amy and Penny. (S9 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Viewing Party Combustion: During a get-together to watch TV at the flat, a minor argument between Sheldon and Leonard escalates into a heated debate. (S9 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Fermentation Bifurcation: The gang run into Penny's ex-boyfriend, Zack, at a wine bar. Bernadette, who can't drink, hangs out with Sheldon. (S9 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great Christmas Bake Off 2021
E4Plus1.uk.description: The stars of It's A Sin join Paul Hollywood, Prue Leith, Matt Lucas and Noel Fielding to celebrate Christmas. And the London Community Gospel Choir perform All I Want for Christmas.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Whacking Day: Lisa asks singer Barry White to help stop the cruel Springfield 'Whacking Day' tradition of hitting snakes with sticks. (S4 Ep20/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Krusty Gets Cancelled: When Krusty's show gets axed, Bart and Lisa enlist Bette Midler, Hugh Hefner, the Red Hot Chili Peppers and Elizabeth Taylor to help him get it back. (S4 Ep22/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer's Barbershop Quartet: Homer reminisces about the Be Sharps, the barbershop quartet he was in with Barney, Apu and Principal Skinner. Guest starring George Harrison. (S5 Ep1/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Cape Feare: When Sideshow Bob is released from prison after sending Bart threatening letters, the Simpsons are moved to Terror Lake under the witness relocation programme. (S5 Ep2/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer Goes to College: Homer has to go to university to study nuclear physics when it becomes clear that he's unqualified for his job as nuclear power plant safety inspector. (S5 Ep3/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox Festive Special
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers watch top Christmas telly, from Jamie's Easy Christmas to Top Gun: Maverick, First Dates at Christmas, Michael McIntyre's Christmas Wheel and much more.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: On the Gogglebox: The Piano, The 1% Club, Inside Windsor Castle, Jack Osbourne's Night of Terror, MILF Manor and ITV News (nightlife & Tory MP defection).  (S23 Ep12) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: This time the Goggleboxers watch: Britain's Got Talent, I Kissed a Girl, Beat the Chasers Celebrity Special, MILF Manor, Marcus Wareing Simply Provence and The Yorkshire Vet. (S23 Ep13) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Is tai chi enthusiast John the yin to dominatrix Sherry's yang? And can karaoke crooner David help Jenni overcome her dating nerves by serenading her at the table? (S8 Ep12) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Political activist Lettie knows a lot about politics but is clueless on love. Her date is Cambridge graduate Fred. And octogenarian Doreen meets author James. (S9 Ep1) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers watch top Christmas telly, from Jamie's Easy Christmas to Top Gun: Maverick, First Dates at Christmas, Michael McIntyre's Christmas Wheel and much more.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Adam Graduates!: Graduation is approaching and everyone, especially Adam, is ready - except for Beverly who's not coping well with the idea of an empty nest. (S9 Ep22)

Film4.uk.description: (2013) Sci-fi thriller. A young programmer agrees to help a reclusive genius to test whether his lifelike android has consciousness, with dramatic results. Strong language/violence.

Film4.uk.title: Men
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Alex Garland's graphic, gory horror with Jessie Buckley and Rory Kinnear. A traumatised woman tries to find solace in the English countryside only to encounter some very odd men.

Film4.uk.title: Let Him Go
Film4.uk.description: (2020) Neo-western with Kevin Costner. After losing their only son, a retired sheriff and his wife try to save their former daughter-in-law from her abusive partner.

Film4.uk.title: Think Like a Dog
Film4.uk.description: (2020) Cheeky comedy with Megan Fox. A young science prodigy (Gabriel Bateman) invents a piece of tech that lets him and his pet dog communicate with each other telepathically.

Film4.uk.title: Mysterious Island
Film4.uk.description: (1961) Sci-fi adventure based on Jules Verne's novel. Two men fleeing the US Civil War find an island inhabited by monsters (animated by Ray Harryhausen) and the mysterious Captain Nemo.

Film4.uk.title: Enemy Mine
Film4.uk.description: (1985) Sci-fi adventure starring Dennis Quaid and Louis Gossett Jr. A human and his alien enemy find themselves stranded alone on a hostile planet, where they must work together to survive.

Film4.uk.title: Men in Black: International
Film4.uk.description: (2019) Fourth instalment of the sci-fi comedy franchise with Chris Hemsworth, Tessa Thompson and Liam Neeson. An alien-obsessed rookie joins London's Men in Black team.

Film4.uk.title: Nobody
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Action thriller with Bob Odenkirk. He's just a dad who goes to work and takes out the trash. But really he's an ex-assassin about to unleash his true self... and take out the trash.

Film4.uk.title: Monster Hunter
Film4.uk.description: (2020) Paul WS Anderson's sci-fi action starring Milla Jovovich, based on the game of the same name. A US Army Ranger must fight her way out of a parallel world full of monsters.

Film4.uk.description: ...Talking Film: Stars and directors talk about the experience of making movies in this compendium of personal and practical reflections.

Film4.uk.title: Sister Act
Film4.uk.description: (1992) Comedy starring Whoopi Goldberg. A casino singer who witnesses a Mob murder goes into hiding at a convent, where she soon has the choir rocking. With Maggie Smith.

Film4.uk.title: Sister Act 2: Back in the Habit
Film4.uk.description: (1993) Comedy sequel starring Whoopi Goldberg and Lauryn Hill. Deloris - who's now made it big in Vegas - goes back undercover as a teacher to help a struggling school choir find its voice.

Film4.uk.title: Ghost Rider
Film4.uk.description: (2007) Nicolas Cage is Marvel's soul-hunting, hot-headed-biker antihero. When Mephistopheles's son starts causing trouble in hell, Ghost Rider is forced to sort it out. With Peter Fonda.

Film4.uk.title: The Last of the Mohicans
Film4.uk.description: (1992) Action adventure starring Daniel Day-Lewis and Madeleine Stowe. Can a frontiersman protect two British women from the brutality of the 18th-century American colonial wars?

Film4.uk.title: Black Sea
Film4.uk.description: (2014) Jude Law stars in Kevin Macdonald's undersea heist. A gang of British and Russian salvage experts aim to illegally snatch gold from a sunken WWII submarine.

Film4.uk.title: Dad's Army

Film4.uk.title: Fatherhood
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Heartfelt fact-based comedy-drama. Kevin Hart stars as a widower who is suddenly sprung into single fatherhood after his wife dies a day after giving birth.

Film4.uk.title: Free Guy
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Comedy action starring Ryan Reynolds. Guy lives in Free City. Free City isn't real. Nor is Guy. It's all a big online game. Can he take down the corrupt game publisher?

Film4.uk.title: Salt
Film4.uk.description: (2010) Action-thriller starring Angelina Jolie. A CIA agent goes on the run after a Russian defector claims that she's a sleeper agent who's about to commit a terrible act of terrorism.
